My style: alt+abcd... means open some window or tools(my convention).
Mac:Atom & IntelliJ & phpstorm & code
Common:
cmd-d delete selected lines
cmd-shift-d duplecate lines
cmd-right forward
cmd-left back
cmd-up move line up
cmd-down move line down
cmd-e extend selection
cmd-shift-e shrink selection
cmd-L 选取1行，继续按，会继续选取下一行
cmd-delete 删除当前字符到行首
cmd-shift-delete 删除当前字符到行尾
cmd-shift-f 全局查找
cmd-z undo
cmd-shift-z redo
cmd-f find
cmd-r replace
ctrl-` open terminal

Atom:
ctrl-enter 光标下面新建一行
ctrl-tab switch tabs
ctrl-| tooggle tree
Not very common:
搜索文件 cmd p
打开一个目录 cmd o
跳转到指定行 ctrl g
ctrl-shift-enter 光标上面新建一行

IntelliJ:
cmd-e extend selection
cmd-shift-e shrink selection
cmd-ctrl-f format
cmd-shift-uparrow move line up
cmd-shift-downarrow move line down
alt-t open terminal
alt-m open Maven Projects
alt-r run
alt-d debug
menu-navigate:
cmd-alt-leftarrow back
cmd-alt-rightarrow forward
cmd-ctrl-leftarrow last edit location
cmd-ctrl-rightarrow next edit location

phpstorm:
cmd-n find class
cmd-shift-n find file
alt-f12 open internal terminal
shift-f6 rename multiple variables
cmd-shift-left last edit location
cmd-shift-right next edit location

visual studio code:
cmd-right move to end of the line
cmd-left move to start of the line
